When we declare a variable for the first time, we should definitely mention datatypes in front of them.

Eg.
int mark; // declaration

int mark = 98; // declaration and assignment in single line

int mark; // declaration
mark = 98; // assignment

In a program, When We declare a variable for the first time, We should mention the datatype in front of them.

